0the%20police%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Udupi%20District%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20HA%20Machindra%20categorically%20denied%20the%20social%20media%20allegations.%20He%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BNot%20a%20single%20video%20connected%20to%20this%20case%20has%20been%20uploaded%20on%20the%20internet.%20On%20the%20contrary%2C%20old%20videos%20have%20been%20wrongfully%20edited%20and%20uploaded%2C%20falsely%20linking%20them%20to%20this%20case.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActing%20of%20its%20own%20accord%2C%20the%20Malpe%20police%20registered%20a%20case%2C%20and%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20was%20filed%20on%20Wednesday%20against%20the%20three%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20the%20turmoil%2C%20an%20alternative%20theory%20has%20emerged%2C%20suggesting%20that%20the%20mobile%20phone%20was%20planted%20in%20the%20washroom%20as%20part%20of%20a%20prank%20intended%20for%20a%20friend.%20This%20misadventure%20spiralled%20out%20of%20control%20when%20another%20student%20found%20the%20device.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConfronted%20with%20the%20device%2C%20the%20accused%20reportedly%20deleted%20the%20video%20on%20the%20spot.%20The%20matter%20was%20deemed%20resolved%20until%20the%20student%20informed%20her%20family%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20subsequent%20suspension%20of%20the%20three%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Home%20Minister%20Dr%20G%20Parameshwara%20appeared%20to%20back%20the%20theory%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BThat%20is%20a%20small%20incident.%20Reports%20say%20it%20happened%20amongst%20friends.%20Should%20it%20be%20blown%20out%20of%20proportion%20and%20given%20a%20political%20colour%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWeren't%20these%20things%20happening%20in%20the%20past%3F%20Weren't%20these%20things%20happening%20in%20the%20past%20in%20colleges%20and%20universities%3F%20No%20one%20did%20politics%20then%2C%20why%20are%20they%20doing%20it%20now%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chief%20Minister%20B