or-thier-censor-certificate%2Fphotostory%2F102139886.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22J%26K's%20Unemployment%20Rate%20Is%20A%20Staggering%2018.3%25.%20The%20National%20Average%20Is...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20unemployment%20rate%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20on%20a%20steady%20rise%2C%20stands%20at%20a%20staggering%2018.3%20per%20cent%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20informed%20Rajya%20Sabha%20today.%20The%20national%20average%2C%20interestingly%2C%20stands%20at%20around%20eight%20per%20cent%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20estimates%20for%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20specifically%20among%20the%20educated%20are%20not%20available%20for%20the%20period%20between%20April%20and%20June%202021.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20according%20to%20a%20survey%20conducted%20between%20July%202020%20and%20June%202021%2C%20the%20estimate%20of%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20among%20the%20people%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2015-29%20years%20was%2018.3%20per%20cent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20Nityanand%20Rai%2C%20told%20the%20Upper%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20in%20J%26amp%3BK%20has%20introduced%20several%20initiatives%20to%20bring%20down%20unemployment%2C%20implementing%20various%20self-employment%20schemes%20through%20different%20departments%2C%20and%20providing%20subsidized%20loans%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20sustainable%20income%20generation%20units%2C%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeveral%20self-employment%20schemes%20like%20Mission%20Youth%2C%20Rural%20Livelihood%20Mission%2C%20Himayat%2C%20PMEGP%2C%20Avsar%2C%20Tejaswani%20are%20being%20implemented%20to%20provide%20employment%20opportunities%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Rai%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MHA%20also%20informed%20the%20parliament%20that%20the%20government%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20has%20carried%20out%20several%20governance%20reforms%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20area%20of%20recruitment%20to%20the%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%2C%20a%20large-scale%20recruitment%20drive%20was%20carried%20out%20and%20the%20government%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20filled%2029%2C295%20vacancies.%20Recruiting%20agencies%20advertised%207%2C924%20vacancies%20and%20examinations%20with%20respect%20to%202%2C504%20were%20conducted%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20written%20reply%20tabled%20in%20parliament%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20identification%20of%20vacancies%20in%20the%20government%20and%20recruitment%20is%20a%20continuous%20and%20ongoing%20process.%20The%20same%20was%20taken%20up%20under%20the%20Accelerated%20Recruitment%20Drive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20upward%20trend%20of%20unemployment%20in%20the%20UT%2C%20a%20senior%20bureaucrat%20explained%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20unemployment%20crisis%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20is%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20retrenchment%20of%20employees%2C%20mergers%20of%20government%20departments%2C%20and%20slacked%20recruitment%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crisis%2C%20fuelled%20by%20multifarious%20reasons%2C%20cannot%20be%20seen%20in%20isolation%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%2C%20%26quot%3BPolitical%20instability%2C%20safety%20issues%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20educational%20and%20industrial%20infrastructure%20have%20had%20its%20effects%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20region.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690373820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fg5et1fg_unemployment_625x300_01_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjammu-and-kashmir-unemployment-rate-is-a-staggering-18-3-the-national-average-is-4242006%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20unemployment%20rate%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20on%20a%20steady%20rise%2C%20stands%20at%20a%20staggering%2018.3%20per%20cent%2C%20the%20Ministry%2