%20light%20after%20a%20video%20went%20viral%20on%20July%2019.%20It%20finally%20forced%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20break%20his%20silence%20on%20the%20riots%20that%20have%20been%20going%20on%20for%20nearly%20three%20months.%20The%20chief%20minister%20also%20spoke%20up%20and%20promised%20action%20against%20the%20culprits.%20The%20incident%20is%20reminiscent%20of%20how%20violence%20in%20Noakhali%20was%20acknowledged%20by%20the%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20Bengal%2C%20Huseyn%20Shaheed%20Suhrawardy%2C%20only%20after%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20camped%20there%20and%20toured%20the%20district%20in%20a%20mission%20to%20restore%20communal%20harmony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%201946%20Noakhali%20riot%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20the%20most%20brutal%20episode%20of%20violence%20in%20pre-partition%20India.%20It%20was%20organised%20against%20the%20minority%20Hindus%20by%20the%20majority%20Muslim%20community%20in%20a%20planned%20manner%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20incumbent%20All%20India%20Muslim%20League%20government%20of%20the%20region.%20Following%20the%20call%20for%20Direct%20Action%20Day%20by%20Mohammad%20Ali%20Jinnah%20demanding%20a%20separate%20Pakistan%2C%20a%20spate%20of%20violence%2C%20pogroms%2C%20looting%20and%20killing%20of%20Hindus%20in%20Calcutta%20erupted%20which%20continued%20for%20several%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20violence%20had%20government%20patronage%2C%20the%20victims%20received%20no%20help.%20Congress%20workers%20also%20felt%20helpless.%20Getting%20no%20support%20from%20outside%2C%20the%20Hindus%20decided%20to%20organise%20themselves%20into%20groups%20and%20took%20up%20arms%20against%20the%20Muslims.%20The%20League%20could%20not%20tolerate%20it%20and%20hence%20the%20Noakhali%20riots%20were%20planned%20in%20revenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoakhali%20was%20a%20Muslim-majority%20district%20in%20the%20Chittagong%20division.%20Here%2C%20the%20Hindu%20minority%20were%20mostly%20%3Cem%3Ezamindars%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20possessed%20vast%20tracts%20of%20land.%20The%20riots%20continued%20for%20several%20days.%20Reports%20of%20violence%20and%20killings%20were%20continuously%20reaching%20Delhi%20but%20no%20one%20could%20tell%20the%20actual%20magnitude%20of%20the%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20made%20Gandhi%20anxious%20despite%20the%20Bengal%20government%20denying%20all%20reports%20of%20violence%20and%20claiming%20that%20things%20were%20normal.%20Even%20the%20Congress%20leaders%20in%20Calcutta%20had%20no%20clue%20of%20the%20real%20situation.%20Finally%2C%20one%20day%20Bapu%20asked%20the%20Congress%20president%20in%20his%20evening%20prayer%20meeting%20to%20visit%20the%20district%2C%20even%20if%20he%20faced%20a%20threat%20to%20his%20life.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20J.B.%20Kripalani%20left%20for%20Calcutta%20accompanied%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20Sucheta%20Kripalani%2C%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20reached%20Calcutta%2C%20the%20state%20Congress%20president%20told%20them%20that%20the%20rioters%20had%20blocked%20all%20routes%20to%20Noakhali%20and%20it%20was%20impossible%20to%20visit%20it.%20He%20refused%20to%20accompany%20Kripalani%20out%20of%20fear.%20When%20Kripalani%20met%20Suhrawardy%2C%20the%20latter%20maintained%20his%20stance%20that%20the%20situation%20was%20fine%20and%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20go%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20discouraged%20so%2C%20the%20Kripalanis%20managed%20to%20reach%20the%20district%20only%20to%20find%20that%20a%20large%20number%20of%20Hindus%20had%20been%20killed%20there.%20Dead%20bodies%20had%20piled%20up%20everywhere.%20Hindus%20had%20been%20forcefully%20evicted%20and%20their%20homes%20were%20captured.%20Forced%20religious%20conversions%20had%20been%20carried%20out.%20In%20addition%20to%20abduction%2C%20rape%20and%20sexual%20violence%2C%20girls%20were%20forced%20to%20convert%20and%20married%20off.%20Temples%20were%20pulled%20down.%20The%20ploughs%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ezamindars%3C%2Fem%3E%20were%20set%20on%20fire%20and%20their%20oxen%20were%20slaughtered%20and%20cooked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20Hindus%20who%20had%20managed%20to%20save%20themselves%20were%20so%20scared%20that%20they%20were%20hiding%20in%20clusters%20of%202-3%20families%20sharing%20a%20single%20room%20along%20with%20their%20animals.%20They%20remained%20hungry%20and%20thirsty%20for%20several%20days.%20There%20was%20not%20a%20single%20police%20or%20administrative%20official%20in%20the%20area.%20After%20taking%20stock%20of%20the%20situation%20for%20three%20days%2C%20J.B.%20Kripalani%20returned%20to%20Delhi.%20But%20Sucheta%20Kripalani%20stayed%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20when%20both%20of%20them%20decided%20to%20leave%2C%20a%20few%20Hindus%20requested%20JB%20to%20allow%20his%20wife%2C%20a%20motherly%20figure%20for%20the%20victims%2C%20to%20stay%20with%20them.%20Their%20pitiful%20exhortation%20left%20the%20couple%20speechless%20and%20Sucheta%20remained%20there%20for%20six%20months%20until%20Gandhi%20arrived%20there%20on%20November%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExcept%20forced%20conversions%2C%20the%20events%20that%20unfolded%20in%20the%20violence%20against%20the%20Kuki%20community%20and%20women%20in%20Manipur%20bear%20stark%20similarity%20to%20the%20Noakhali%20riots.%20Sexual%20violence%20against%20women%20started%20as%20soon%20as%20ethnic%20violence%20erupted%20in%20the%20region%20on%20May%203.%20But%20neither%20the%20chief%20minister%20nor%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20nor%20the%20governor%20of%20Manipur%20who%20is%20a%20woman%2C%20nor%20the%20peace%20committee%20nor%20any%20army%20officer%2C%20even%20suggested%20that%20women%20were%20being%20subjected%20to%20violence%20there%20or%20made%20any%20effort%20to%20stop%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20does%20this%20signify%3F%20Back%20then%20it%20was%20Suhrawardy%20who%20kept%20assuring%20everyone%20that%20everything%20was%20fine.%20And%20here%2C%20it%20was%20the%20%E2%80%98let%20things%20be%E2%80%99%20attitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20spate%20of%20violent%20attacks%20against%20women%20happened%20one%20after%20the%20other%20in%20May.%20Especially%20in%20Kuki-dominated%20area%20Churachandpur.%20Organised%20sexual%20violence%20and%20gang%20rape%20was%20perpetrated%20against%20them%20by%20members%20of%20the%20majority%20Meitei%20community.%20According%20to%20the%20statements%20given%20by%20the%20Kuki%20rape%20victims%2C%20Meitei%20women%20were%20also%20inciting%20the%20mob%20to%20commit%20sexual%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20happened%20because%20on%20May%204%2C%20fake%20news%20was%20spread%20that%20Kuki%20men%20had%20raped%20a%20Meitei%20woman%20in%20Churachandpur.%20On%20May%205%2C%20the%20Inspector%20General%20of%20Police%20denied%20the%20news.%20The%20father%20of%20the%20girl%20who%20was%20believed%20to%20have%20been%20raped%20also%20denied%20the%20reports.%20But%20by%20then%20the%20crowd%20had%20gone%20berserk.%20In%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20it%20was%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20police%20and%20the%20administration%20to%20pacify%20the%20people%20by%20taking%20them%20into%20confidence%2C%20but%20no%20such%20efforts%20were%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Kuki%20women%20whose%20video%20has%20gone%20viral%20allege%20that%20the%20police%20themselves%20brought%20them%20out%20of%20the%20village%20and%20handed%20them%20over%20to%20the%20mob.%20The%20husband%20of%20one%20of%20these%20women%20lodged%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20police%20station%20on%20May%2018%2C%20but%20no%20action%20was%20taken.%20The%20police%20(reluctantly)%20arrested%20the%20youth%20seen%20in%20the%20footage%20only%20when%20the%20video%20went%20viral%20after%20more%20than%2070%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20understand%20that%20there%20are%20mainly%20two%20communities%20in%20Manipur%20between%20whom%20there%20is%20an%20ongoing%20tussle.%20One%20is%20the%20Kuki-Zomi%20community%2C%20who%20are%20tribals%2C%20Christian%20and%20dwell%20on%20the%20mountains.%20The%20Meiteis%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20are%20wealthier%20Hindus%20who%20have%20more%20participation%20in%20power%20and%20inhabit%20the%20plain%20areas.%20Now%2C%20the%20Meiteis%20are%20demanding%20that%20they%20be%20declared%20as%20tribal%2C%20which%20would%20mean%20that%20they%20too%20will%20get%20the%20right%20to%20buy%20tribal%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20big%20concern%20for%20Kuki%20and%20other%20tribal%20communities%20because%20it%20will%20make%20the%20Meiteis%20even%20stronger.%20The%20conflict%20of%20interest%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20is%20quite%20old.%20Needless%20to%20mention%2C%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20is%20also%20a%20Meitei.%20If%20he%20wanted%2C%20he%20could%20have%20used%20his%20influence%20to%20pacify%20his%20community%2C%20at%20least%20in%20the%20matter%20of%20women.%20But%20when%20it%20is%20about%20Hindu%20nationalism%2C%20then%20a%20free%20rein%20has%20to%20be%20given.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20is%20happening.%20Had%20the%20ill-fated%20video%20not%20come%20to%20the%20fore%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20would%20still%20be%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20when%20he%20spoke%2C%20he%20dragged%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20say%20that%20the%20violence%20in%20Manipur%20has%20brought%20shame%20to%20the%20country.%20Wrong.%20What%20has%20put%20us%20to%20shame%20is%20a%20prime%20minister%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20the%20difference%20between%20everyday%20rape%20incidents%20and%20deliberate%20sexual%20violence%20carried%20out%20as%20part%20of%20caste%20riots.%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20his%20statements%20are%20enough%20to%20enrage%20any%20sensitive%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20chief%20minister%20chose%20to%20remain%20silent%20and%20the%20governor%20depended%20on%20social%20media%20for%20information%2C%20how%20could%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%2C%20Rekha%20Sharma%2C%20question%20the%20Manipur%20police%20and%20the%20administration%3F%20Two%20women%20from%20Manipur%20and%20the%20Manipur%20Tribal%20Association%2C%20whose%20headquarters%20are%20abroad%2C%20had%20informed%20the%20Commission%20about%20such%20incidents%20through%20a%20letter%20mailed%20on%20June%2012.%20Believing%20the%20Commission%20to%20be%20the%20protector%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20honour%2C%20and%20constitutional%20and%20human%20rights%2C%20they%20requested%20it%20to%20take%20suo%20moto%20cognisance%20of%20the%20incidents%2C%20take%20action%20and%2C%20if%20possible%2C%20set%20up%20an%20inquiry%20committee.%20But%20they%20did%20not%20even%20receive%20an%20acknowledgment%20of%20the%20mail%20from%20the%20Commission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mail%20should%20have%20sufficed%20for%20Sharma%20to%20take%20action%20and%20send%20the%20commission%E2%80%99s%20representatives%20to%20the%20spot%20to%20get%20the%20matter%20investigated.%20But%20it%20was%20the%20video%20which%20evoked%20some%20sort%20of%20a%20response%20from%20her%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20hasty%20tweet.%20If%20a%20tweet%20had%20the%20power%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20would%20not%20have%20despatched%20a%20large%20number%20of%20central%20forces%20there.%20Clearly%2C%20Sharma%20missed%20the%20chance%20to%20win%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20trust%20and%20pacify%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESwati%20Maliwal%2C%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Commission%2C%20has%20announced%20that%20she%20will%20visit%20the%20state%2C%20but%20the%20question%20is%20whether%20she%20will%20be%20able%20to%20carry%20out%20any%20work%20without%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20Centre%2C%20considering%20the%20Delhi%20government%E2%80%99s%20relationship%20with%20the%20Centre%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20talk%20about%20the%20media.%20Most%20of%20the%20major%20newspapers%20and%20TV%20channels%20in%20Manipur%20belong%20to%20the%20Meitei%20community%20and%20are%20not%20reporting%20much%20about%20the%20violence%20against%20the%20Kukis.%20The%20%3Cem%3ESangai%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20newspaper%20went%20so%20far%20as%20to%20call%20the%20community%20%E2%80%98alien%E2%80%99.%20But%20the%20national%20media%20also%20received%20information%20about%20the%20organised%20sexual%20violence%20happening%20in%20the%20state%20only%20through%20the%20viral%20video.%20Why%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20leave%20aside%20TV%20channels%20based%20in%20Delhi%20as%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20deem%20it%20important%20enough%20to%20be%20discussed%20even%20after%20they%20had%20received%20information.%20By%20doing%20so%2C%20they%20have%20demonstrated%20that%20anarchy%20is%20acceptable%20to%20them.%20If%20it%20were%20not%20so%2C%20the%20love%20affair%20of%20Seema%20Haider%2C%20who%20eloped%20from%20Pakistan%2C%20would%20not%20have%20been%20the%20primetime%20story%20on%20every%20channel%20bar%20a%20few.%20Why%20did%20major%20English%20newspapers%2C%20with%20a%20network%20in%20the%20North-East%20as%20well%2C%20fail%20to%20find%20out%20about%20the%20violence%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20detailed%20report%20on%20sexual%20violence%20in%20the%20state%20was%20published%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20July%2012.%20Earlier%2C%20%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20published%20an%20article%20on%20June%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20calls%20for%20the%20media%20to%20introspect.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20peace%20is%20really%20to%20be%20established%20in%20Manipur%2C%20then%20someone%20will%20have%20to%20camp%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20way%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20did%20in%20Noakhali.%20He%20went%20there%20with%20his%20entire%20team%2C%20stayed%20there%20for%20three%20months%20and%20surveyed%20the%20area%20barefoot.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20the%20entire%20land%20had%20become%20a%20crematorium%20for%20its%20people%20and%20walking%20on%20it%20with%20shoes%20on%20would%20be%20an%20insult%20to%20them.%20He%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20bring%20himself%20to%20do%20so.%20He%20stayed%20at%20the%20houses%20of%20Muslim%20attackers%20and%20inspired%20them%20to%20help%20resettle%20the%20Hindus%20back%20in%20their%20houses.%20He%20got%20them%20to%20embrace%20each%20other%20by%20removing%20the%20mistrust%20and%20hatred%20between%20the%20two%20communities.%20Peace%20and%20relief%20committees%20were%20set%20up.%20He%20left%20the%20place%20only%20after%20things%20had%20calmed%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20of%20Noakhali%20and%20the%20restoration%20of%20peace%20in%20the%20region%20by%20Gandhi%20are%20both%20remarkable%20events%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India.%20We%20must%20learn%20from%20our%20past.%20The%20Kukis%20of%20Manipur%20are%20in%20a%20state%20of%20fear%20today%20similar%20to%20what%20the%20Hindu%20community%20must%20have%20felt%20in%20Noakhali%20back%20then.%20But%20does%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20have%20anyone%20who%20could%20be%20a%20Gandhi%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20bigger%20question%20is%20whether%20they%20really%20want%20to%20stop%20the%20violence%20happening%20under%20the%20patronage%20of%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20government%20%E2%80%93%20perhaps%20only%20if%20the%20objective%20of%20the%20majoritarian%20violence%20has%20been%20achieved.%20It%20will%20be%20a%20different%20matter%20if%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20intervenes%2C%20as%20the%20chief%20justice%20has%20said%20%E2%80%93%20or%20if%20the%20Kuki%20women%E2%80%99s%20heartfelt%20pleas%20inspire%20the%20president%20to%20issue%20some%20directives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENeelam%20Gupta%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20former%20Adjunct%20Professor%20at%20Gujarat%20Vidyapith%2C%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewirehindi.com%2F254059%2Fmanipur-violence-noakhali-riots-mahatma-gandhi-narendra-modi%2F%5C%22%3EHindi%20original%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690373518000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3