ad%5C%22%3A%20Chief%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAssam%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20claimed%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20a%20triple%20murder%20in%20Golaghat%20was%20a%20result%20of%20'love%20jihad'%2C%20a%20term%20often%20used%20by%20right-wing%20politicians%20to%20allege%20a%20campaign%20by%20Muslim%20men%20to%20convert%20Hindu%20women%20by%20seducing%20them.%20Mr%20Sarma%20assured%20that%20a%20chargesheet%20would%20be%20filed%20within%2015%20days%2C%20with%20the%20intention%20of%20fast-tracking%20the%20trial%20of%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20total%20case%20of%20love%20jihad.%20The%20deceased%20family%20was%20Hindu%20and%20the%20accused%20belongs%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20He%20first%20introduced%20himself%20with%20a%20Hindu%20name%20on%20Facebook...%20the%20woman%20learnt%20to%20use%20drugs%20when%20the%20couple%20had%20escaped%20to%20Kolkata%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20said%20during%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20family%20of%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20victims%20were%20identified%20as%20Sanjeev%20Ghosh%2C%20Junu%20Ghosh%2C%20and%20Sanghamitra%20Ghosh.%20Their%20bodies%20were%20found%20with%20multiple%20injuries%2C%20suggesting%20they%20were%20attacked%20with%20sharp%20weapons%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20that%20the%20accused%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20mechanical%20engineer%20identified%20as%20Najibur%20Rahman%20Bora%2C%20was%20a%20drug%20addict%20and%20involved%20in%20trafficking%20contraband%20substances.%20%26quot%3BThe%20woman%20was%20given%20injectable%20drugs%2C%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20which%20she%20was%20impregnated.%20She%20was%20tortured%20when%20she%20went%20to%20live%20at%20the%20house%20of%20the%20accused%20and%20returned%20to%20her%20maternal%20home%20later%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20expressed%20concern%20over%20cases%20where%20religious%20identities%20are%20hidden%20to%20influence%20women%20into%20marriage%2C%20leading%20to%20situations%20where%20societal%20acceptance%20becomes%20difficult%20if%20the%20woman%20decides%20to%20return.%20%26quot%3BIn%20such%20a%20situation%2C%20she%20ultimately%20converts%20her%20religion%2C%20sacrifices%20everything%20and%20assimilates%20into%20a%20different%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20murder%20of%20his%20wife%20and%20her%20parents%2C%20Bora%20surrendered%20to%20the%20police%20in%20the%20Golaghat%20district%20of%20Upper%20Assam.%20%26quot%3BA%20proper%20investigation%20will%20be%20conducted%2C%20and%20I%20hope%20that%20further%20details%20will%20be%20revealed%20after%20that...%20We%20will%20take%20the%20strictest%20possible%20action%20and%20no%20one%20will%20be%20spared%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20said%2C%20amid%20questions%20about%20the%20potential%20involvement%20of%20other%20family%20members%2C%20specifically%20the%20accused's%20brother%20and%20mother.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sarma%2C%20who%20also%20heads%20the%20Home%20Department%2C%20described%20it%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bopen-and-shut%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20plans%20to%20file%20the%20chargesheet%20within%20the%20next%2015%20days.%20He%20later%20tweeted%2C%20reaffirming%20the%20Assam%20government's%20commitment%20to%20making%20the%20society%20a%20zero-crime%20place%2C%20stating%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20criminal%20shall%20escape%20justice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20received%20a%20letter%20from%20Ankita%2C%20the%20sister-in-law%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20about%20the%20incident%20but%20had%20missed%20it%20due%20to%20the%20volume%20of%20correspondence%20he%20receives.%20The%20letter%2C%20he%20said%2C%20had%20been%20sent%20during%20the%20lockdown%20period%20resulting%20from%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20circumstances%20were%20different%20then%20as%20the%20lockdown%20was%20in%20place%2