itive%20results%20from%20a%20clinical%20trial%20by%20Mirati%2C%20an%20oncology%20company%2C%20via%20an%20employee%20at%20his%20hedge%20fund%20who%20sat%20on%20Mirati's%20board.%20Lewis%2C%20one%20of%20Mirati's%20biggest%20shareholders%2C%20urged%20a%20girlfriend%20of%20his%2C%20his%20two%20private%20pilots%2C%20his%20executive%20assistant%2C%20a%20person%20he%20was%20romantically%20involved%20with%2C%20and%20a%20person%20he%20occasionally%20played%20poker%20with%20in%20Argentina%20to%20buy%20Mirati%20stock%2C%20per%20the%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20indictment%2C%20Lewis%20even%20gave%20his%20pilots%20%24500%2C000%20each%20in%20short-term%20loans%20so%20that%20they%20could%20buy%20stock%20before%20the%20news%20became%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20also%20says%C2%A0that%2C%20as%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20shareholders%20in%20Solid%20Biosciences%2C%20Lewis%20was%20given%20confidential%20information%20about%20an%20upcoming%20announcement%20of%20favorable%20clinical%20results.%20Under%20advice%20from%20Lewis%20to%20buy%20the%20company's%20stock%20before%20the%20news%20became%20public%2C%20his%20girlfriend%20and%20two%20pilots%20bought%20shares%2C%20per%20the%20indictment.%20The%20company's%20stock%20went%20up%20after%20the%20clinical%20results%20were%20released%2C%20and%20the%20girlfriend%20made%20a%20profit%20of%20around%20%24849%2C000%2C%20a%20118%25%20gain%2C%20according%20to%20the%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20instance%2C%20Lewis%20gave%20his%20two%20pilots%20a%20tip-off%20about%20how%20flooding%20in%20Queensland%20in%20early%202019%20had%20caused%20material%20financial%20losses%20to%20Australian%20Agricultural%20Company%2C%20the%20indictment%20says.%20Lewis%2C%20who%20owned%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20company's%20stock%2C%20got%20non-public%20information%20from%20a%20Tavistock%20employee%20who%20sat%20on%20its%20board%20that%20the%20cattle%20deaths%20and%20financial%20losses%20wouldn't%20be%20covered%20by%20its%20insurance%20or%20the%20Australian%20government%2C%20per%20the%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELewis%20shared%20this%20information%20with%20the%20two%20pilots%20and%20urged%20them%20to%20sell%20off%20their%20stock%2C%20according%20to%20the%20indictment.%20The%20company's%20stock%20fell%20the%20next%20day%20after%20it%20publicly%20announced%20its%20losses%2C%20but%20the%20pilots'%20stockbroker%20couldn't%20sell%20their%20shares%20quickly%20enough%2C%20according%20to%20the%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20wish%20the%20Boss%20would%20have%20given%20us%20a%20little%20earlier%20heads%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20pilots%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20their%20stockbroker%2C%20per%20the%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20also%20says%20that%20Lewis%20conspired%20with%20others%20and%20used%20a%20series%20of%20shell%20companies%2C%20false%20filings%2C%20and%20misleading%20statements%20to%20hide%20his%20ownership%20of%20shares%20in%20Mirati.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20indictment%20asks%20Lewis%20to%20forfeit%20all%20property%20linked%20to%20proceeds%20from%20the%20transactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInsider%20has%20approached%20Lewis's%20lawyer%2C%20Tottenham%20Hotspur%2C%20and%20the%20Tavistock%20Group%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20at%20the%20time%20of%20publication%2C%20had%20not%20received%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoe-lewis-charged-insider-trading-pilots-assistants-tottenham-hotspurs-tavistock-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690371141000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c0f37e671ed6001915505b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjoe-lewis-charged-insider-trading-pilots-assistants-tottenham-hotspurs-tavistock-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20indictment%20claims%20that%20Tottenham%20Hotspur%20owner%20Joe%20Lewis%20lent%20his%20pilots%20%24