2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Worst%20cardboard-box%20recession%20since%202008%20could%20be%20a%20sign%20of%20broader%20economic%20weakness%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20dog%20sits%20in%20an%20Amazon%20cardboard%20box%20shaped%20into%20an%20airplane%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c0d8b01f17bb00196e40d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECardboard-box%20sales%20have%20seen%20the%20biggest%20contraction%20since%20the%20Great%20Recession%20of%202008-2009.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPackaging%20Corp.%20of%20America%20just%20reported%20an%20almost%2010%25%20year-on-year%20slump%20in%20second-quarter%20shipments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECardboard%2C%20often%20overlooked%2C%20can%20be%20a%20reliable%20economic%20indicator%20given%20its%20key%20role%20in%20e-commerce%20and%20the%20shipping%20of%20goods.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20months%20now%2C%20a%20debate%20has%20been%20raging%20among%20experts%20whether%20the%20US%20economy%20is%20facing%20a%20recession%2C%20following%20the%20Federal%20Reserve's%20steepest%20interest-rate%20increases%20in%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20they%20have%20used%20all%20kinds%20of%20gauges%20%E2%80%93%20from%20job-market%20numbers%20to%20the%20shape%20of%20the%20bond-yield%20curve%20%E2%80%93%20to%20argue%20in%20support%20of%20and%20against%20predictions%20for%20a%20potential%20downturn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20rather%20offbeat%20indicator%20has%20been%20signaling%20a%20level%20of%20economic%20weakness%20not%20seen%20since%20the%20global%20financial%20crisis%20of%202008-2009%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that's%20the%20shipments%20of%20cardboard%20boxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPackaging%20Corp.%20of%20America%2C%20the%20No.%203%20containerboard%20company%20in%20the%20US%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fir.packagingcorp.com%2Fnews-releases%2Fnews-release-details%2Fpackaging-corporation-america-reports-second-quarter-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20this%20week%20that%20sales%20of%20cardboard%20boxes%20fell%209.8%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20quarter%20from%20a%20year%20earlier%20in%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20slumps%20on%20record.%20That%20added%20to%20a%2012.7%25%20plunge%20during%20the%20first%20quarter.%20The%20combined%20six-month%20decline%20is%20the%20biggest%20since%20early%202009%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20FreightWaves%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thinking%20goes%20that%20cardboard%20boxes%20can%20act%20as%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22929fddbeace8036bccc7d8bd04f5f299%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2260%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Fstory%2F2022-12-22%2Fworld-cardboard-boxes-bad-sign-economy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20barometer%20for%20the%20health%20of%20the%20economy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20since%20they%20play%20such%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20transporting%20goods%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20to%20consumers%20who%20buy%20things%20online%2C%20but%20to%20stores%20and%20warehouses%20that%20receive%20those%20goods%20in%20bulk.%20That%20means%20that%20if%20demand%20for%20cardboard%20is%20slowing%2C%20consumers%20are%20buying%20less%20stuff.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Fed's%20aggressive%20interest-rate%20increases%20have%20curbed%20demand%20for%20cardboard%20boxes%20over%20the%20past%20year%20and%20demand%20may%20enter%20a%20prolonged%20slump%2C%20according%20to%20FreightWaves%2C%20a%20supply-chain%20intelligence%20firm.%20The%20Fed%20has%20raised%20benchmark%20rates%20by%20500%20basis%20points%20since%20early%202022%20to%20tame%20historically%20high%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20outlook%20for%20cardboard%20box%20shipments%20continues%20to%20be%20cloudy%2C%20according%20to%20FreightWaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20regional%20banks%20cutting%20back%20on%20lending%20out%20of%20necessity%2C%20the%20emergency%20government%20food%20stamp%20(SNAP)%20benefits%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past%2C%20federal%20student%20loan%20payments%20set%20to%20resume%20in%20October%20and%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20continuing%20to%20tighten%20monetary%20policy%20to%20combat%20inflation%2C%20we're%20unsure%20what%20would%20lead%20to%20improved%20box%20demand%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20see%20the%20slide%20in%20cardboard%20box%20shipments%20as%20a%20sign%20of%20broader%20economic%20trouble.%20Danielle%20DiMartino%20Booth%2C%20CEO%20of%20QI%20research%2C%20tweeted%20ironically%20in%20response%20to%20the%20Packaging%20Corp.%20results%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20recession%3F%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPackaging%20Corp.%20sales%20have%20now%20seen%20year-on-year%20declines%20for%20the%20fourth%20consecutive%20quarter%2C%20which%20could%20also%20be%20a%20sign%20of%20demand%20returning%20to%20pre-pandemic%20levels%20after%20an%20exceptional%20two-year%20spike.%20But%20for%20those%20who%20see%20cardboard%20as%20a%20crucial%20barometer%20of%20health%20for%20the%20US%20economy%2C%20this%20spells%20only%20bad%20news.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworst-cardboard-box-recession-since-2008-warns-of-broader-downturn-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690370526000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c0d8b01f17bb00196e40d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworst-cardboard-box-recession-since-2008-warns-of-broader-downturn-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cardboard-box%20sales%20have%20seen%20the%20biggest%20contraction%20since%20the%20Great%20Recession%20of%202008-2009.%20Packaging%20Corp.%20of%20America%20just%20reported%2