al%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102138593%2Cimgsize-157452.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fno-confidence-motion-against-modi-government-the-numbers-in-lok-sabha-oppositions-battle-of-perception%2Farticleshow%2F102138603.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fno-confidence-motion-against-modi-government-the-numbers-in-lok-sabha-oppositions-battle-of-perception%2Farticleshow%2F102138603.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Behind%20the%20Scenes%20Look%20at%20Organising%20the%20First%20Ever%20IPL%20Tournament%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162447%2FWith-Virender-Sehwag-captain-Delhi-Daredevils-2008.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EPutting%20things%20together%20was%20particularly%20challenging%20because%20nothing%20in%20Delhi%20is%20easy.%20It%20is%20a%20city%20with%20a%20flourishing%20VIP%20culture%20where%20everyone%20is%20a%20heavyweight%20ready%20to%20throw%20their%20weight%20around.%20Delhi%20is%20about%20power%20and%20entitlement%3B%20it%20is%20about%20government%20regulations%20and%20people%20who%20must%20be%20%E2%80%98obliged%E2%80%99.%20Holding%20a%20commercial%20cricket%20tournament%20in%20such%20an%20environment%20tested%20the%20notion%20of%20the%20ease%20of%20doing%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20working%20with%20the%20DDCA%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easy.%20It%20had%20a%20well-earned%20reputation%20as%20a%20divided%20house%20constantly%20in%20a%20state%20of%20civil%20war%20and%20internal%20insurgency.%20The%20silver%20lining%20in%20the%20otherwise%20dark%20scenario%20was%20Arun%20Jaitley%2C%20the%20one-man%20DRS%20(dispute%20resolution%20system)%20who%2C%20whenever%20there%20was%20a%20disagreement%2C%20heard%20your%20appeal%20for%20relief%20and%20fair%20play%20and%20passed%20a%20nuanced%20judgement.%20Jaitley%E2%80%99s%20intervention%20was%20needed%20often%20because%20the%20IPL%20disturbed%20the%20power%20equation%20within%20state%20associations.%20During%20the%20IPL%2C%20control%20of%20stadium%20facilities%20shifted%20from%20association%20officials%20to%20team%20owners%2C%20a%20change%20resented%20by%20the%20local%20cricket%20dons%20because%20it%20meant%20the%20tenants%20were%20calling%20the%20shots%20instead%20of%20the%20landlords.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20395px)%2085vw%2C%20395px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162543%2FPitchside_Front.jpg_page-0001.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22395%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162543%2FPitchside_Front.jpg_page-0001.jpg%20794w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162543%2FPitchside_Front.jpg_page-0001-199x300.jpg%20199w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162543%2FPitchside_Front.jpg_page-0001-678x1024.jpg%20678w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665251%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22597%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAmrit%20Mathur%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EPitchside%3A%20My%20Life%20in%20Indian%20Cricket%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3EWestland%20Sport%2C%202023%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20IPL%20demanded%20%E2%80%98world-class%E2%80%99%20standards%20and%20a%20good%20%E2%80%98fan%20experience%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20ground%20was%20another%20reason%20for%20franchise%20teams%20to%20sweat.%20The%20IPL%20small%20print%20included%20designer%20invites%2C%20a%20consistent%20%E2%80%98look%20and%20feel%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20fine%20dining%20with%20customised%20crockery%20and%20branded%20napkins.%20The%20league%20was%20positioned%20as%20the%20big%20fat%20Indian%20wedding%3A%20grand%20in%20scale%2C%20full%20of%20glitter%20and%20glamour%2C%20noisy%20and%20garish.%20The%20IPL%20matches%20were%20pitched%20as%20events%2C%20concept%20that%20was%20very%20different%20from%20the%20ordinary%20BCCI%20games%20where%20it%20was%20enough%20to%20mark%20the%20wicket%20and%20get%2022%20players%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kotla%20infrastructure%20was%20not%20even%20remotely%20world-class.%20The%20ground%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20floodlights%20or%20essential%20facilities%20for%20spectators.%20The%20Delhi%20Daredevils%20hired%20a%20cleaning%20agency%20a%20month%20before%20Kotla%E2%80%99s%20first%20IPL%20match%20in%202008%20to%20get%20the%20stadium%20spruced%20up%20in%20time.%20We%20discovered%2C%20not%20to%20our%20surprise%2C%20that%20there%20were%20parts%20of%20the%20ground%20that%20had%20not%20met%20a%20brush%20or%20a%20bottle%20of%20cleaning%20liquid%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecuring%20permissions%20to%20stage%20the%20event%20was%20also%20sheer%20torture.%20Several%20government%20agencies%20had%20to%20be%20satisfied%20(police%2C%20entertainment%20tax%2C%20electricity%20and%20water%2C%20fire%2C%20disaster%20management)%20and%20getting%20the%20paperwork%20done%20eventually%20boiled%20down%20to%20delicate%20negotiations%20over%20free%20tickets%20and%20passes.%20In%20Delhi%2C%20managing%20the%20distribution%20of%20freebies%20is%20a%20highly%20valued%20skill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20an%20operations%20standpoint%2C%20besides%20the%20standard%20drill%2C%20one%20had%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20the%20anti-dew%20treatment%20before%20an%208%20a.m.%20game%20and%20fogging%20the%20playing%20area%20to%20keep%20mosquitos%20away.%20Generators%20had%20to%20be%20hired%20to%20guard%20against%20power%20failure%20and%20security%20guards%20were%20hired%20to%20guard%20the%20generators%20and%20prevent%20sabotage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20deployed%20almost%202%2C000%20personnel%20for%20overall%20security%2C%20background%20checks%20of%20people%20and%20sanitising%20the%20stadium.%20On%20match%20days%2C%20sniffer%20dogs%20checked%20the%20premises%20and%20scanners%2C%20metal%20detectors%20and%20CCTVs%20were%20installed%20at%20strategic%20points.%20Security%20was%20strict%20to%20the%20point%20where%20spectators%20were%20not%20allowed%20to%20bring%20pens%20or%20coins%20into%20the%20stadium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20frantic%20efforts%20to%20tie%20up%20all%20the%20loose%20ends%20we%20came%20close%20to%20breaking%20point%20on%20many%20occasions.%20The%20accreditation%20system%20collapsed%20just%20before%20the%20first%20home%20game%2C%20leading%20to%20extreme%20panic%20because%2C%20without%20proper%20IDs%2C%20the%20police%20refused%20to%20allow%20players%2C%20umpires%20and%20the%20ground%20staff%20in.%20When%20the%20ticket%20box%20office%20opened%20at%20Dr%20Ambedkar%20Stadium%2C%20the%20rush%20was%20such%20that%20the%20police%20had%20to%20be%20called%20to%20restore%20order.%20Some%20scalpers%20were%20arrested%20for%20selling%20tickets%20in%20%E2%80%98black%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20development%20which%20led%20to%20an%20investigation%20to%20determine%20whether%20franchise%20insiders%20were%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImagine%20also%20the%20horror%20when%20we%20were%20left%20with%20unsold%20tickets%20for%20lower-end%20seats%20for%20some%20games.%20As%20empty%20stands%20look%20bad%20on%20television%2C%20schoolchildren%20were%20bussed%20into%20the%20stadium%20and%20given%20free%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chaos%20in%20the%20exclusive%20hospitality%20areas%20was%20even%20more%20troubling.%20The%20high-end%20corporate%20boxes%20were%20marketed%20as%20a%20khaana-peena-daaru%20deal%20that%20promised%20five-star%20catering%20and%20premium%20liquor.%20The%20strategy%20worked.%20However%2C%20an%20unexpected%20snag%20developed%20when%20hordes%20of%20gatecrashers%20invaded%20the%20hospitality%20boxes.%20Security%20broke%20down%2C%20drunken%20brawls%20took%20place%20and%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20registered%20a%20case%20of%20public%20disorder%2C%20unruly%20behaviour%20and%20hooliganism.%20A%20concerned%20senior%20officer%20gave%20me%20friendly%20advice%3A%20Free%20daaru%20ko%20roko.%20Yeh%20Dilli%20culture%20mein%20nahi%20chalta.%20Arun%20Jaitley%20supported%20the%20liquor%20ban%20for%20a%20similar%20reason.%20During%20the%20matches%2C%20his%20box%20was%20full%20of%20uninvited%20guests%20who%20raided%20the%20food%20counter%20and%20polished%20off%20the%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162802%2FIPL-Match-Delhi.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22620%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162802%2FIPL-Match-Delhi.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162802%2FIPL-Match-Delhi-300x279.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26162802%2FIPL-Match-Delhi-1024x951.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665253%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22575%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAt%20an%20IPL%20match%20in%20Delhi.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnable%20to%20control%20this%2C%20he%20switched%20to%20a%20strict%20no%20alcohol%2C%20only%20soft%20drinks%E2%80%99%20policy%20in%20his%20box.%20This%20worked%3A%20the%20number%20of%20Gate%20crashers%20dropped%20and%20order%20was%20restored.By%20the%20end%20of%20the%20first%20IPL%20season%20four%20FIRs%20had%20been%20filed%20against.%20Me%2C%20the%20Daredevils%E2%80%99%20chief%20operating%20officer%2C%20for%20black%20marketing%20of%20tickets%2C%20overcharging%20for%20food%20items%20in%20the%20stadium%2C%20betting%20on%20games%2C%20and%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98indecent%20behaviour%