ormance-hunk-says-ive-been-knighted%2Farticleshow%2F102132820.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Only%20Two-Thirds%20of%20Hospitals%20Under%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Scheme%20Active%20Now%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F30121127%2Fayushman-bharat-digital-mission.png%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20More%20than%20a%20third%20of%20hospitals%20empanelled%20under%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20are%20inactive%2C%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fover-a-third-of-hospitals-empanelled-under-ayushman-bharat-scheme-in-new-delhi-are-inactive-official-data-11690305764552.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20studying%20official%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20notes%20that%20this%20data%20is%20updated%20daily%20and%20at%20present%2C%2018%2C783%20out%20of%20the%2027%2C000%20hospitals%20under%20the%20scheme%20are%20active.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20(PM-JAY)%20has%20been%20touted%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnha.gov.in%2FPM-JAY%5C%22%3Ethe%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20health%20assurance%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20aims%20to%20provide%20health%20cover%20of%20Rs.%205%20lakhs%20per%20family%20per%20year%20for%20secondary%20and%20tertiary%20care%20hospitalisation%20to%20over%2012%20crores%20poor%20and%20vulnerable%20families%2C%20covering%20approximately%2055%20crore%20beneficiaries%20that%20form%20the%20bottom%2040%25%20of%20the%20Indian%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20households%20included%20are%20based%20on%20the%20deprivation%20and%20occupational%20criteria%20of%20Socio-Economic%20Caste%20Census%202011%20(SECC%202011)%20for%20rural%20and%20urban%20areas%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EMint%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said%20that%204%2C682%20hospitals%20had%20been%20inactive%20since%202018%2C%20when%20the%20scheme%20was%20introduced%2C%20and%20had%20not%20served%20a%20single%20scheme%20beneficiary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20notes%20that%20as%20many%20as%203%2C632%20hospitals%20only%20turned%20inactive%20in%20the%20last%20six%20months.%20It%20is%20not%20mentioned%20if%20this%20sudden%20surge%20was%20due%20to%20delayed%20tallying%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20insurance%20scheme%20was%20just%20one%20component%20of%20Ayushman%20Bharat.%20The%20other%20had%20promised%20the%20creation%20of%201%2C50%2C000%20health%20and%20wellness%20centres%20(HWCs)%20by%20transforming%20the%20existing%20sub-centres%20and%20primary%20health%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690366862000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F09%2F30121127%2Fayushman-bharat-digital-mission.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fayushman-bharat-scheme-inactive-hospitals%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20'Mint'%20report%20said%20that%204%2C682%20hospitals%20out%20of%20the%2027%2C000%20originally%20empanelled%2C%20had%20been%20inactive%20since%202018%2C%20when%20the%20scheme%20was%20introduced%2C%20and%20had%20not%20served%20a%20single%20scheme%20beneficiary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fayushman-bharat-scheme-inactive-hospitals%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Names%20of%20More%20Than%205%20Crore%20Deleted%20From%20MGNREGS%20in%20FY%202022-23%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F07101954%2F7655150258_021e6c9ffd_o.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20State%20governments%20across%20the%20country%20have%20deleted%20the%20names%20of%205.18%20crore%20workers%20registered%20under%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Scheme%20(MGNREGS)%20in%20the%20financial%20year%202022-2023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20represents%20a%20247%25%20increase%20in%20deletions%20compared%20to%20the%20last%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnion%20rural%20development%20minister%20Giriraj%20Singh%20provided%20these%20statistics%20through%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scribd.com%2Fdocument%2F661244349%2FJuly-25-reply-by-Ministry-of-Rural-Development-on-MGNREGS-deletions%5C%22%3Ewritten%20reply%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20July%2025%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%E2%80%99s%20reply%20stated%20that%20there%20were%20many%20reasons%20for%20the%20deletions%2C%20including%20%E2%80%9C1.%20fake%20job%20card%20(incorrect%20job%20card)%2C%202.%20duplicate%20job%20card%2C%203.%20now%20not%20willing%20to%20work%2C%204.%20family%20shifted%20from%20gram%20panchayat%20permanently%2C%20and%205.%20single%20person%20in%20job%20card%20and%20the%20person%20is%20expired%20%5Bsic%5D.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20by%20Congress%20MPs%20V.K.%20Sreekandan%20and%20Gourav%20Gogoi%20asking%20if%20it%20was%20true%20that%20over%20a%20crore%20names%20had%20been%20deleted%20from%20the%20MGNREGS%20system%2C%20and%20if%20so%2C%20why.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20MGNREGS%20guarantees%20100%20days%20of%20employment%20to%20rural%20households%20in%20the%20country%20at%20specially%20notified%20minimum%20wages.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWork%20under%20the%20scheme%20involves%20physical%20labour%20and%20includes%20activities%20such%20as%20construction%2C%20afforestation%20and%20land-levelling.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESingh%20clarified%20in%20his%20response%20that%20%E2%80%9Csystem%20error%E2%80%9D%20was%20not%20a%20defined%20reason%20for%20the%20deletions.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fparliament-proceedings-names-of-over-five-crore-mgnregs-workers-deleted-in-2022-23-minister-tells-lok-sabha%2Farticle67120001.ece%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20a%20reason%20for%20the%20deletions%20is%20that%20state%20governments%20are%20unable%20to%20reconcile%20differences%20in%20the%20details%20of%20registered%20workers%20between%20their%20MGNREGS%20job%20cards%20and%20Aadhaar%20cards.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELabourers%20have%20had%20to%20link%20these%20two%20cards%20because%20the%20Union%20government%20decided%20earlier%20this%20year%20to%20route%20payments%20for%20the%20MGNREGS%20mandatorily%20through%20Aadhaar%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20biometric%20identification%20system.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Faadhaar-payments-compulsory-nrega%5C%22%3EMaking%20Aadhaar-Based%20Payments%20Compulsory%20for%20NREGA%20Wages%20Is%20a%20Recipe%20for%20Disaster%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20government%20has%20extended%20its%20deadline%20for%20this%20%E2%80%98Aadhaar-based%20payment%20system%E2%80%99%20to%20become%20compulsory%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fdeadline-for-aadhaar-based-payments-for-mnregs-workers-extended-to-august-31%2Farticle67015415.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emultiple%20times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20since%20January%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20these%20extensions%20did%20not%20stop%20state%20governments%20%E2%80%9Cracing%20against%20the%20timeline%E2%80%9D%20from%20%E2%80%9Cresorting%20to%20removing%20%5Bfrom%20the%20MGNREGS%20system%5D%20%E2%80%A6%20workers%20who%20have%20discrepancies%20between%20the%20two%2