twcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fvariety.com%252F2023%252Fmusic%252Fnews%252Ftony-bennett-elton-john-reaction-tribute-1235676405%252F%5C%22%3EHarry%20Connick%20Jr.%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20come%20as%20no%20surprise.%20Yes%2C%20Bennett%20was%20a%20jazz%20crooner.%20But%20if%20his%20voice%20was%20always%20a%20constant%20%E2%80%93%20even%20late%20into%20his%2080s%2C%20way%20past%20an%20age%20when%20most%20other%20singers%20have%20seen%20their%20vocal%20abilities%20diminish%20%E2%80%93%20then%20his%20embrace%20of%20the%20contemporary%20was%20every%20bit%20a%20facet%20of%20Bennett%E2%80%99s%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVocal%20innovator%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBennett%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20power%20of%20daring%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20early%20days%20of%20his%20career%20in%20the%201950s%20to%20his%20final%20recordings%20in%20the%20early%202020s%2C%20he%20fearlessly%20explored%20new%20musical%20territories%2C%20revolutionising%20vocal%20jazz%20and%20captivating%20audiences%20across%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20vocal%20style%20and%20phrasing%20were%20distinctive%20and%20set%20him%20apart%20from%20other%20artists%20of%20his%20time.%20He%20utilised%20a%20delayed%20or%20%E2%80%9Claid-back%E2%80%9D%20approach%20to%20falling%20on%20the%20note%2C%20a%20technique%20known%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.musictheoryacademy.com%2Fhow-to-read-sheet-music%2Frubato%2F%5C%22%3Erubato%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%20This%20created%20a%20sense%20of%20anticipation%20in%20his%20phrasing%2C%20adding%20an%20element%20of%20surprise%20to%20his%20performances.%20Through%20Bennett%E2%80%99s%20skilled%20use%20of%20rubato%2C%20he%20was%20able%20to%20play%20with%20the%20tempo%20and%20rhythm%20of%20a%20song%2C%20bending%20and%20stretching%20musical%20phrases%20to%20evoke%20a%20range%20of%20emotions.%20This%20subtle%20manipulation%20of%20timing%20gave%20his%20songs%20a%20natural%20and%20conversational%20quality%2C%20making%20listeners%20feel%20as%20though%20he%20was%20intimately%20sharing%20his%20stories%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20this%20silky%2C%20playful%20voice%2C%20Bennett%20found%20fame%20fairly%20early%20on%20in%20his%20career%2C%20delivering%20jazz%20standards%20alongside%20the%20likes%20of%20Mel%20Torm%C3%A9%20and%20Nat%20King%20Cole.%20By%20the%20mid-1960s%2C%20he%20was%20being%20touted%20by%20Frank%20Sinatra%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20best%20singer%20in%20the%20business.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20musical%20style%20fell%20out%20of%20fashion%20in%20the%201970s%20%E2%80%93%20a%20lean%20period%20during%20which%20Bennett%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fhistory%2F2023%2F07%2F21%2Ftony-bennett-son-life-career-drugs%2F%5C%22%3Ealmost%20succumbed%20to%20a%20drug%20overdose%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Then%2C%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20Bennett%20found%20a%20new%20audience%20and%20set%20off%20a%20series%20of%20collaborations%20with%20contemporary%20musical%20stars%20that%20would%20become%20the%20standard%20for%20his%20later%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20genre%20of%20artistry%20was%20deemed%20off-limits%20for%20Bennett.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tonybennett.com%2Fmusic-detail.php%3Fid%3D11%5C%22%3EDuets%3A%20An%20American%20Classic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20released%20to%20coincide%20with%20his%2080th%20birthday%20in%202006%2C%20saw%20collaborations%20with%20country%20stars%20such%20as%20k.d.%20lang%20and%20the%20Dixie%20Chicks%20%E2%80%93%20now%20known%20as%20the%20Chicks%20%E2%80%93%20and%20soul%20legend%20Stevie%20Wonder%2C%20alongside%20kindred%20jazz%20spirits%20such%20as%20Diana%20Krall.%20%E2%80%9CDuets%20II%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%202011%20follow-up%2C%20saw%20further%20explorations%20with%20the%20likes%20of%20Aretha%20Franklin%2C%20Queen%20Latifah%2C%20Willie%20Nelson%20and%20Amy%20Winehouse%2C%20in%20what%20would%20become%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffaroutmagazine.co.uk%2Famy-winehouse-final-recording-session%2F%5C%22%3EBritish%20singer%E2%80%99s%20last%20recording%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20cross-generational%2C%20cross-genre%20and%20cross-cultural%20appeal%20is%20perhaps%20best%20exemplified%20by%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F07%2F21%2Farts%2Fmusic%2Ftony-bennett-lady-gaga.html%5C%22%3Ecollaborations%20with%20Lady%20Gaga%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20first%20on%20the%202014%20Grammy-winning%20album%20%E2%80%9CCheek%20to%20Cheek.%E2%80%9D%20The%20recording%20brought%20together%20two%20artists%20from%20different%20generations%2C%20genres%20and%20backgrounds%2C%20uniting%20them%20in%20a%20harmonious%20celebration%20of%20jazz%20classics.%20The%20collaboration%20not%20only%20showcased%20each%20one%E2%80%99s%20vocal%20prowess%2C%20but%20also%20sent%20a%20powerful%20message%20about%20the%20unifying%20nature%20of%20music.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELady%20Gaga%2C%20a%20pop%20artist%20with%20avant-garde%20leanings%2C%20might%20have%20seemed%20an%20unlikely%20partner%20for%20Bennett%2C%20the%20quintessential%20jazz%20crooner.%20Yet%20their%20musical%20chemistry%20and%20mutual%20admiration%20resulted%20in%20an%20album%20that%20mesmerised%20audiences%20worldwide.%20%E2%80%9CCheek%20to%20Cheek%E2%80%9D%20effortlessly%20transcended%20musical%20boundaries%2C%20while%20the%20duo%E2%80%99s%20magnetic%20stage%20presence%20and%20undeniable%20talent%20enchanted%20listeners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20successful%20fusion%20of%20jazz%20and%20pop%20encouraged%20artists%20to%20experiment%20beyond%20traditional%20boundaries%2C%20leading%20to%20more%20cross-genre%20projects%20across%20the%20industry%20%E2%80%93%20proving%20that%20such%20projects%20could%20go%20beyond%20one-off%20novelties%2C%20and%20be%20profitable%20at%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETimeless%20artistry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBennett%E2%80%99s%20embrace%20of%20contemporary%20artists%20did%20not%20mean%20that%20he%20abandoned%20his%20own%20musical%20self.%20By%20blending%20traditional%20jazz%20with%20contemporary%20elements%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20captivate%20audiences%20across%20generations%2C%20appealing%20to%20both%20longtime%20fans%20and%20new%20listeners.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20key%20aspect%20of%20Bennett%E2%80%99s%20success%20was%20his%20ability%20to%20embody%20the%20sentiment%20of%20old%20America%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20artists%20like%20Sinatra%2C%20Billie%20Holiday%20and%20Louis%20Armstrong%2C%20while%20infusing%20contemporary%20nuances%20that%20resonated%20with%20the%20human%20condition%20of%20a%20more%20modern%20era.%20His%20approach%20to%20music%20captured%20both%20the%20essence%20and%20struggle%20of%20America%2C%20giving%20his%20songs%20a%20timeless%20and%20universal%20appeal.%20Moreover%2C%20his%20voice%20conveyed%20familiarity%20and%20comfort%2C%20akin%20to%20listening%20to%20a%20beloved%20uncle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBennett%E2%80%99s%20albums%20stood%20out%20not%20only%20for%20his%20soulful%20voice%20and%20impeccable%20delivery%20but%20also%20for%20the%20way%20he%20drew%20others%20from%20varied%20musical%20backgrounds%20into%20his%20world%20of%20jazz%20sensibilities.%20As%20a%20producer%2C%20he%20recognised%20the%20importance%20of%20nurturing%20creativity%20and%20bringing%20out%20the%20best%20in%20artists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Bennett%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20evolving%20his%20own%20sound%20while%20preserving%20its%20essence%20sets%20him%20apart%20as%20an%20artist.%20Fearless%20in%20his%20pursuit%20of%20innovation%2C%20he%20delved%20into%20contemporary%20musical%20elements%20and%20collaborated%20with%20producers%20to%20infuse%20new%20sonic%20dimensions%20into%20his%20later%20albums.%20The%20result%20drew%20listeners%20into%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6kNpdLZwetU%5C%22%3Eintimate%20and%20immersive%2C%20concert-like%20acoustic%20journey%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDepth%20of%20emotion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20greats%20in%20music%20have%20an%20ability%20to%20speak%20to%20the%20human%20experience.%20And%20either%20in%20collaboration%20with%20others%20or%20on%20his%20own%2C%20Bennett%20was%20able%20to%20achieve%20this%20time%20and%20time%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20albums%20were%20successful%20not%20only%20due%20to%20their%20technical%20brilliance%20and%20musicality%20but%20also%20because%20Bennett%E2%80%99s%20voice%20conveyed%20a%20depth%20of%20emotion%20that%20transcended%20barriers%20of%20time%20and%20culture%2C%20touching%20the%20hearts%20of%20listeners%20from%20various%20backgrounds.%20There%20was%20a%20universality%20in%20his%20music%20that%20made%20him%20a%20beloved%20and%20revered%20artist%20across%20the%20globe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBennett%E2%80%99s%20life%20spanned%20decades%20of%20societal%20upheavals%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20But%20in%20his%20music%2C%20listeners%20could%20always%20find%20beauty%20in%20challenging%20times.%20And%20as%20the%2020th-%20and%2021st-century%20American%20music%20industry%20went%20through%20its%20own%20revolutions%2C%20Bennett%E2%80%99s%20artistic%20evolution%20mirrored%20the%20changes%2C%20cementing%20his%20place%20as%20a%20music%20icon%20who%20defies%20the%20boundaries%20of%20time%20and%20trends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJose%20Valentino%20Ruiz%2C%20Program%20Director%20of%20Music%20Business%20%26amp%3B%20Entrepreneurship%2C%20University%20of%20Florida.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Ftony-bennett-the-timeless-visionary-who-with-a-nod-to-americas-musical-heritage-embraced-the-future-210244%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690365705000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2