-conferred-with-frances-highest-award-grand-cross-of-the-legion-of-honour%2Farticle67078793.ece%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPrime%2520Minister%2520Narendra%2520Modi%2520has%2Cby%2520French%2520President%2520Emmanuel%2520Macron.%5C%22%3EFrench%20Legion%20of%20Honour%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20joyfully%20given%2C%20joyfully%20received.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20beleaguered%20state%20of%20Manipur%20some%20rioters%20were%20issued%20warrants%20and%20hauled%20to%20prisons.%20Who%20were%20they%3F%20What%20sections%20were%20slapped%3F%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnarendra-modi-islamic-nations-egypt-eid-gujarat-lynching%5C%22%3EEgypt%E2%80%99s%20Paeans%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%20Cannot%20Erase%20the%20Past%20or%20Present%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20nation%20I%20feel%20we%20must%20demand%20%E2%80%98command%20responsibility.%E2%80%99%20This%20concept%20is%20used%20in%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice.%20Responsibility%20lies%20with%20the%20highest%20authority.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiving%20life%20sentences%2C%20even%20hanging%20a%20few%20is%20relatively%20easy.%20They%20are%20the%20rogue%20perpetrators.%20But%20their%20strings%20are%20held%20by%20those%20at%20the%20pinnacle.%20By%20shouting%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ekhoon%20ka%20badla%20khoon%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0from%20the%20rooftops%20we%2C%20the%20masses%20cannot%20be%20lulled%3B%20we%20are%20alive%20and%20awake.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E*%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%20is%20the%20land%20which%20gave%20birth%20to%20Polo%2C%20Sagol%20Kangjei%2C%20in%20ancient%20days.%20In%201799%20to%20it%20birthed%20Rasleela.%20I%20remember%20watching%20a%20breathtaking%20performance%20in%20the%20then%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20was%20r