s%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fnarendra-modi-islamic-nations-egypt-eid-gujarat-lynching%5C%22%3EEgypt%E2%80%99s%20Paeans%20to%20Narendra%20Modi%20Cannot%20Erase%20the%20Past%20or%20Present%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20nation%20I%20feel%20we%20must%20demand%20%E2%80%98command%20responsibility.%E2%80%99%20This%20concept%20is%20used%20in%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice.%20Responsibility%20lies%20with%20the%20highest%20authority.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiving%20life%20sentences%2C%20even%20hanging%20a%20few%20is%20relatively%20easy.%20They%20are%20the%20rogue%20perpetrators.%20But%20their%20strings%20are%20held%20by%20those%20at%20the%20pinnacle.%20By%20shouting%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ekhoon%20ka%20badla%20khoon%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0from%20the%20rooftops%20we%2C%20the%20masses%20cannot%20be%20lulled%3B%20we%20are%20alive%20and%20awake.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E*%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EManipur%20is%20the%20land%20which%20gave%20birth%20to%20Polo%2C%20Sagol%20Kangjei%2C%20in%20ancient%20days.%20In%201799%20to%20it%20birthed%20Rasleela.%20I%20remember%20watching%20a%20breathtaking%20performance%20in%20the%20then%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20home.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20state%20was%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Jewel%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%99%20encircled%20by%20nine%20hills%20with%20an%20oval%20shaped%20valley%20in%20the%20centre.%20I%20walked%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Manipur%20at%20the%20time%20of%20Kangla%20festivities%20as%20well%20as%20the%20time%20when%20Thangjam%20Manorma%20was%20gang%20raped%20and%20killed%20and%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20stripped%20before%20the%20garrison%20of%20Assam%20Rifles%20in%20protest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F03%2FManipur-mothers-reuters.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%