am%20and%20Meghalaya%20felt%20like%20another%20Karbala%20to%20me.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20healers%20and%20mourners%2C%20we%20want%20to%20place%20our%20loving%20hands%20on%20the%20wounds%20inflicted%20on%20our%20Manipur%20sisters%20and%20brothers.%20Imphal%2C%20Bishnupur%2C%20Churachandpur%2C%20Thoubal%2C%20Senapati%3B%20where%20to%20date%20there%20have%20been%20at%20least%20150%20deaths%2C%201%2C000%20injured%20and%2050%2C000%20homeless.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%2C%20the%20people%20of%20India%20have%20just%20one%20goal%20and%20an%20arduous%20path%20to%20tread.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20words%20of%20Faiz%20Ahmed%20Faiz%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EKat-te%20bhi%20chalo%20badhte%20bhi%20chalo%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBaazu%20bhi%20bahaut%20hain%20sar%20bhi%20bahaut%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EChalte%20bhi%20chalo%20ke%20ab%20derey%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EManzil%20pe%20hi%20daale%20jayeinge%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E(Keep%20proceeding%2C%20keep%20falling%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20many%20arms%20many%20heads%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKeep%20moving%20for%20tents%20will%20be%20pitched%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20only%20at%20the%20destination)%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESyeda%20Hameed%20is%20a%20writer%20and%20the%20founder%20chair%20of%20the%20Muslim%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Forum.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690364918000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F12114331%2F33F81A3F-BCF6-4D05-975C-264958F029F4_1_105_c.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthere-has-to-be-command-responsibility-for-manipur%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Manipur%20is%20not%20the%20first%20h