ates-ntpc-land-subsidence-cracks%2F%5C%22%3Eblame%20the%20excavation%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20undertaken%20as%20part%20of%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Tapovan%20Vishnugad%20hydel%20power%20project%20%E2%80%93%20a%20520-megawatt%20dam%20%E2%80%93%20as%20one%20cause%20for%20the%20sinking%20of%20their%20town.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fsupreme-court-char-dham-highway-national-security-wider-landslide-prone-roads-uttarakhand%5C%22%3Econstruction%20of%20the%20Char%20Dham%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20an%20ambitious%20900%20km-long%20all-weather%20road%20through%20the%20state%20to%20promote%20religious%20tourism%20%E2%80%93%20is%20also%20a%20cause%2C%20according%20to%20experts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20time%20around%20the%20incessant%20rains%20in%20Uttarakhand%20for%20the%20last%2015%20days%20have%20also%20contributed%20to%20the%20latest%20episode%20of%20cracks.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20situation%20has%20become%20even%20more%20fragile%20during%20the%20rainy%20season%20and%20the%20administration%20and%20the%20government%20should%20take%20steps%20on%20a%20war%20footing%20towards%20Joshimath%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ved%20Prakash%20Pant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHighways%20in%20the%20state%20are%20the%20worst%20affected%20due%20to%20rains.%C2%A0Badrinath%20National%20Highway%20near%20Kalimati%20was%20damaged%20in%20landslides%20near%20Gauchar%20and%20Kameda.%C2%A0The%20authorities%20concerned%20closed%20a%20total%20of%20362%20roads%2C%20including%20four%20national%20highways%20across%20the%20state%2C%20to%20avert%20accidents%20and%20to%20carry%20out%20repair%20works.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rains%20have%20also%20badly%20affected%20the%20movement%20on%20the%20Joshimath-Malari%20highway%2C%20which%20connects%20to%20the%20China%20border%20area.%20Chamoli%20district%20authorities%20said%20the%20road%20is%20in%20bad%20condition%20at%20several%20points%2C%20and%20vehicular%20movement%20is%20being%20affected%20due%20to%20debris%20