re%20-%20what%20to%20do%2C%20what%20not%20to%20do%2C%20respect%20the%20sea%20lions%2C%20don't%20touch%20them%2C%20don't%20get%20in%20their%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20Japhet%20Perez%20Estrada%2C%20a%20La%20Jolla%20native%20and%20business%20owner%2C%20said%20to%20FOX%205%20on%20Monday.%20He%20swims%20the%20cove%20every%20day%20and%20captured%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20as%20he%20was%20getting%20out%20of%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20looked%20to%20my%20left%20and%20I%20see%20a%20big%20sea%20lion%20just%20come%20out%20of%20the%20water%20and%20start%20charging%20and%20that's%20when%20it%20turns%20to%20chaos%2C%26quot%3B%20Perez%20Estrada%20said.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20was%20screaming%20and%20running%20around.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20is%20going%20viral%20on%20the%20internet.%20While%20some%20users%20said%20that%20humans%20should%20not%20encroach%20on%20their%20space%2C%20others%20said%20that%20sea%20lions%20were%20likely%20chasing%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20blame%20them%20at%20all.%20Humans%20are%20a%20darn%20pestilence%20on%20this%20earth%20and%20the%20sealions%20know%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20user%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20absolutely%20encroaching%20on%20their%20space%20I%20despair%20...%20they%20are%20stressed%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERobyn%20Davidoff%2C%20chair%20of%20the%20Sierra%20Club%20Seal%20Society%20told%20Fox%20News%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20sea%20lion%20world%2C%20this%20is%20mating%20season%20and%20the%20males%20are%20trying%20to%20establish%20territory%2C%20both%20in%20the%20water%20and%20on%20land.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20do%20that%20by%20pushing%20the%20other%20one%20out%20of%20the%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESea%20lions%20are%20amazing%20creatures%20and%20their%20videos%20get%20a%20huge%20hit%20on%20the%20internet.%20A%20few%20days%2C%20the%20video%20of%20a%20sea%20lion%20nearly