%20be%20sold%20to%20any%20person%20below%20the%20age%20of%2025%2C%20while%20in%20Haryana's%20Gurugram%2C%20it%20can%20be%20sold%20to%20anyone%20who%20is%20above%2018.%20In%20UP%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20the%20legal%20drinking%20age%20is%2021.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Metro%20trains%20ferry%20commuters%20between%20Delhi%20and%20NCR%20cities%20like%20Noida%2C%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Gurgaon%20and%20Faridabad%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20officer%20of%20Delhi's%20excise%20department%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Excise%20Act%20allows%20only%20one%20sealed%20bottle%20of%20liquor%20like%20rum%2C%20vodka%20and%20whisky%20to%20be%20carried%20from%20one%20state%20to%20another.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20one%20sealed%20bottle%20is%20allowed%20whereas%20in%20Haryana%2C%20the%20limit%20is%20one%20litre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMRC%2C%20on%20its%20part%2C%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20on%20what%20items%20are%20permitted%20for%20carriage%20on%20Metro%20trains%20is%20based%20upon%20permissibility%20by%20the%20security%20agency%20in%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPassengers%20are%20expected%20to%20follow%20extant%20rules%20and%20regulations%20of%20the%20concerned%20state%20excise%20department%20with%20regard%20to%20carrying%20liquor%20during%20cross-border%20transit%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DMRC%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bconcern%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20excise%20department%20will%20be%20conveyed%20to%20the%20security%20agency%20to%20examine%20accordingly%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two-bottle%20norm%20was%20recommended%20by%20a%20committee%20comprising%20DMRC%20and%20Central%20Industrial%20Security%20Force%20(CISF)%2C%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20security%20at%20Metro%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690362960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2Flcqg4qo8_delhi-metro-parting-ways-650_625x300_20_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F