0%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102133383%2Cimgsize-183485.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fankit-tiwari-on-manipur-horror-im-afraid-i-would-think-100-times-before-travelling-with-my-crew-to-a-place-where-such-gut-wrenching-acts-are-committed%2Farticleshow%2F102133439.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102133439.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EMusician%20Ankit%20Tiwari%20recently%20put%20out%20a%20Twitter%20thread%20expressing%20shock%2C%20anger%20and%20disgust%20at%20the%20molestation%20of%20two%20women%20in%20violence%20hit%20Manipur.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20can't%20imagine%20what%20those%20women%20and%20their%20families%20must%20be%20going%20through%20right%20now%20and%20hopes%20that%20the%20culprits%20get%20a%20harsh%20punishment%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fankit-tiwari-on-manipur-horror-im-afraid-i-would-think-100-times-before-travelling-with-my-crew-to-a-place-where-such-gut-wrenching-acts-are-committed%2Farticleshow%2F102133439.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Barring%20the%20Enumeration%20of%20SCs%2C%20STs%2C%20No%20Caste%20Census%20Since%20Independence%3A%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F10105410%2Fpti12082021000100b-1-1058909-1638977919.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Union%20government%20has%20informed%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20that%20caste-wise%20enumeration%20of%20the%20population%20other%20than%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SCs)%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(STs)%20during%20the%20Census%20has%20not%20been%20carried%20out%20since%20Independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20written%20reply%20to%20a%20question%2C%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Home%20Nityanand%20Rai%20told%20the%20parliament%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20July%2025%2C%20that%20castes%20and%20tribes%20which%20are%20specifically%20notified%20as%20SCs%20and%20STs%20as%20per%20the%20Constitution%20(Scheduled%20Castes)%20Order%2C%201950%2C%20and%20the%20Constitution%20(Scheduled%20Tribes)%20Order%2C%201950%2C%20as%20amended%20from%20time%20to%20time%2C%20are%20enumerated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20demand%20from%20various%20political%20parties%20to%20collect%20caste%20details%20of%20all%20communities%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20Census%2C%20Rai%20merely%20acknowledged%20that%20there%20is%20a%20demand%20without%20expanding%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20parties%2C%20including%20social%20justice%20parties%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-caste-census-ideological-unity-opposition%5C%22%3Ehave%20been%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fwhy-the-bjp-is-afraid-of-a-caste-census%5C%22%3Edemanding%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0a%20caste%20census%20on%20a%20national%20basis%20to%20determine%20reservations%20for%20Other%20Backward%20Communities%20(OBCs)%20in%20jobs%20and%20educational%20institutions.%20This%20demand%20has%20been%20a%20significant%20election%20issue%2C%20aimed%20at%20attracting%20OBC%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20maintained%20that%20conducting%20a%20caste%20survey%20during%20the%20national%20census%20is%20challenging%20due%20to%20administrative%2C%20legal%2C%20and%20technical%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Congress-led%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20government%20first%20carried%20out%20a%20Socio-Economic%20and%20Caste%20Census%20(SECC)%20in%202011-12%2C%20it%20has%20never%20been%20released%20because%20of%20varied%20opinions%20about%20the%20data%20within%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-caste-census-ideological-unity-opposition%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20was%20more%20vocally%20expressed%20by%20different%20opposition%20parties%20after%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20implemented%20reservation%20for%20the%20Economically%20Weaker%20Classes%20(EWS)%2C%20which%20effectively%20gave%20a%20quota%20to%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cupper%20caste%E2%80%9D%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20perception%20among%20the%20supporters%20of%20caste-based%20reservation%20that%20EWS%20reservation%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Canomaly%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20caste-based%20affirmative%20action%20policy%20because%20the%20criteria%20is%20poverty%20and%20the%20move%20is%20aimed%20at%20denying%20marginalised%20castes%20and%20communities%20their%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690359926000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F02%2F10105410%2Fpti12082021000100b-1-1058909-1638977919.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbarring-the-enumeration-of-scs-sts-no-caste-census-since-independence-centre%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20demand%20from%20various%20political%20parties%20to%20collect%20caste%20details%20of%20all%20communities%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20Census%2C%20the%20government%20merely%20acknowledged%20that%20there%20is%20a%20demand%20without%20expanding%20further.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbarring-the-enumeration-of-scs-sts-no-caste-census-since-independence-centre%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nitesh%20is%20hurt%20with%20criticism%20to%20Bawaal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690359617000%2C%22