ushan-his-son-not-part-of-electoral-college-for-wfi-polls-but-son-in-law-to-represent-bihar%2Farticleshow%2F102115021.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20wrestler%20Anita%20Sheoran%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20one%20of%20the%20witnesses%20in%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20case%20against%20Singh%2C%20has%20made%20it%20to%20the%20list%20from%20Odisha%20even%20though%20she%20hails%20from%20Haryana%20and%20is%20employed%20with%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20police%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fsport-others%2Ffacing-sexual-harassment-charges-brij-bhushan-excluded-from-wfi-electoral-rolls-son-karan-too-omitted-8860032%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOdisha%20Wrestling%20Association%20secretary%20Kishor%20Behera%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20their%20bylaws%20gave%20them%20an%20option%20of%20nominating%20someone%20from%20outside%20the%20state.%20Anita%20won%20a%20gold%20medal%20at%20the%202010%20Commonwealth%20Games%20in%20the%2067%20kg%20weight%20class%20and%20is%20a%20two-time%20Asian%20medallist.%20%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20our%20bylaws%2C%20we%20can%20name%20someone%20who%20is%20not%20from%20Odisha%20to%20be%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20state%20in%20the%20electoral%20college.%20She%20(Anita)%20is%20an%20established%20wrestler%20and%20we%20hope%20to%20benefit%20from%20her%20experience%2C%E2%80%9D%20Behera%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fsport-others%2Ffacing-sexual-harassment-charges-brij-bhushan-excluded-from-wfi-electoral-rolls-son-karan-too-omitted-8860032%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20Prem%20Chand%20Lochab%20who%20hails%20from%20Rajasthan%20and%20is%20not%20a%20part%20of%20Gujarat%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20executive%20body%20will%20be%20representing%20the%20latter%20alongside%20Brij%20Bhushan%20loyalist%20and%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20body%20president%20I%20D%20Nanavati%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETOI%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20No%20clarification%20has%20been%20given%20for%20how%20Lochan%20is%20eligible%20to%20represent%20Gujarat%20in%20upcoming%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERochab%20is%20employed%20at%20the%20Railways%20Sports%20Promotion%20Board%20(RSPB)%20where%20the%20three%20prominent%20faces%20of%20the%20protest%20against%20Brij%20Bhushan%20%E2%80%93%20Bajrang%20Punia%2C%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Sakshee%20Malikkh%20%E2%80%93%20are%20also%20employed%20and%20report%20directly%20to%20Lochab%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETOI%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20representatives%20from%20each%20state%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20vote%20except%20Maharashtra%20and%20Tripura.%20While%20Maharashtra%20sent%20two%20sets%20of%20nominations%20from%20two%20factions%2C%20which%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fsports%2Fsport-others%2Ffacing-sexual-harassment-charges-brij-bhushan-excluded-from-wfi-electoral-rolls-son-karan-too-omitted-8860032%2F%5C%22%3Efound%20ineligible%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20returning%20officer%2C%20Tripura%20has%20been%20disaffiliated%20from%20the%20WFI%20since%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690356637000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F28201406%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-05-28-at-8.13.23-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwfi-polls-brij-bhushan-son-out-of-electoral-college-son-in-law-to-vote-from-bihar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sports%20minister%20Anurag%20Thakur%20had%20promised%20to%20the%20protesting%20wrestlers%20that%20no%20one%20from%20Brij%20Bhushan's%20family%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20contest%20the%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Fwfi-polls-brij-bhushan-son-out-of-electoral-college-son-in-law-to-vote-from-bihar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%2