22554%2FScreenshot-2023-07-26-at-12.25.33-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESrinagar%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Forty-year-old%20Numina%20Begum%20and%20her%20husband%20Muhammad%20Saleem%2C%20Rohingya%20Muslim%20refugees%20lodged%20in%20the%20lone%20detention%20centre%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20were%20brought%20in%20handcuffs%20on%20July%2019%20to%20attend%20the%20last%20rites%20of%20their%20infant%20child.%20While%20the%20Rohingya%20living%20in%20Jammu%20claim%20that%20the%2040-day-old%20baby%20died%20after%20inhaling%20teargas%20fired%20by%20the%20police%20during%20clashes%20between%20detained%20refugees%20and%20the%20detention%20centre%20staff%20on%20July%2018%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20authorities%20denied%20the%20allegation%2C%20saying%20the%20baby%20had%20not%20been%20keeping%20well%20since%20her%20birth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20authorities%20have%20not%20denied%20the%20use%20of%20teargas%20in%20the%20centre%20where%20the%20baby%20and%20her%20parents%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20death%20of%20a%20Rohingya%20person%20in%20the%20Hira%20Nagar%20detention%20centre%20in%20Kathua%20district%2C%20Jammu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrought%20in%20handcuffs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20several%20videos%20which%20have%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20Numina%20Begum%20and%20her%2017-year-old%20son%20can%20be%20seen%20being%20brought%20in%20handcuffs%20to%20attend%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20funeral%20in%20Jammu%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20of%20the%20videos%2C%20a%20policewoman%20is%20seen%20escorting%20Numina%20Begum%20in%20handcuffs%2C%20while%20a%20few%20women%20from%20the%20Rohingya%20community%20are%20consoling%20her.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20shocked%20to%20see%20them%20in%20handcuffs.%20Saleem%20and%20his%20elder%20son%20were%20handcuffed%20even%20at%20the%20time%20of%20offering%20funeral%20prayers%20for%20the%20baby%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20elder%20community%20member%20from%20Rohingya%20refugees%2C%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20kept%20handcuffed%20here%20for%20nearly%20one%20hour%20and%20then%20take%20back%20to%20the%20detention%20centre.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20even%20hardcore%20criminals%20are%20not%20treated%20like%20this.%20%E2%80%9CAren%E2%80%99t%20we%20(Rohingya)%20humans%3F%20We%20had%20never%20imagined%20that%20we%20would%20be%20subjected%20to%20such%20an%20inhuman%20treatment%20in%20India.%20We%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20protest%20against%20their%20maltreatment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20infant%E2%80%99s%20body%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20house%20of%20Saleem%E2%80%99s%20brother%20on%20Wednesday%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20performing%20ablution%20and%20funeral%20prayers%2C%20the%20baby%20was%20buried%20at%20a%20graveyard%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20official%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Prison%20Department%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Rohingya%20refugees%20kept%20in%20the%20holding%20centre%20cannot%20be%20treated%20like%20prisoners.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20movement%20is%20restricted%20in%20a%20particular%20area%20till%20they%20are%20repatriated%20to%20their%20native%20country%2C%20but%20they%20cannot%20be%20treated%20like%20prisoners.%20Even%20prisoners%20are%20handcuffed%20only%20when%20there%20is%20apprehension%20of%20their%20escape%20or%20if%20they%20are%20dangerous%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20M.S.%20Lone%2C%20former%20DIG%20Prisons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Rules%2C%202021%20prohibit%20handcuffing%20of%20a%20child%20alleged%20to%20be%20in%20conflict%20with%20the%20law.%20This%20raises%20question%20on%20the%20handcuffing%20of%20the%20Rohingya%20couple%E2%80%99s%20elder%20son%2C%20who%20is%20said%20to%20be%2017%20and%20is%20thus%20a%20minor%20as%20per%20Indian%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20baby%E2%80%99s%20death%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rohingya%20living%20in%20Jammu%20claim%20that%20the%20baby%20died%20due%20to%20teargas%20canisters%20fired%20by%20the%20police%20after%20clashes%20between%20refugees%20and%20prison%20staff%20on%20July%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20fired%20teargas%20shells%20to%20quell%20protests%20by%20Rohingya%20refugees%20who%20were%20seeking%20their%20release%20from%20the%20detention%20centre%20or%20their%20immediate%20repatriation%20to%20Myanmar%2C%20despite%20the%20persecution%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20truth%20in%20the%20claims%20that%20the%20baby%20died%20due%20to%20inhalation%20of%20teargas%20canisters%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20superintendent%20district%20jail%20Kathua%20and%20in-charge%20holding%20centre%2C%20Koushal%20Kumar.%20However%2C%20officials%20have%20not%20denied%20that%20teargas%20was%20used%20against%20the%20refugees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaleem%20arrested%20in%202012%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20relatives%2C%20Saleem%20along%20with%20his%20brother%20Fareed%20Alam%20came%20to%20India%20after%20fleeing%20Myanmar%20in%202012%2C%20when%20it%20saw%20large-scale%20violence%20against%20the%20Rohingya.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20forces%20in%20Myanmar%20were%20killing%20and%20torturing%20us.%20We%20ran%20away%20from%20our%20homes%20to%20save%20our%20lives%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Fatima%20Begum%2C%20Saleem%E2%80%99s%20sister-in-law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaleem%2C%20she%20said%2C%20started%20doing%20menial%20jobs%20in%20Jammu%20to%20eke%20out%20a%20livelihood%20for%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20felt%20safe%20here%20and%20were%20content.%20But%20there%20was%20no%20end%20to%20our%20miseries%20as%20Saleem%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20police%20in%20the%20same%20year.%20He%20did%20not%20have%20a%20refugee%20card%20at%20that%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20immediately%20went%20to%20Delhi%20and%20got%20refugee%20cards%2C%E2%80%9Dshe%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20refugee%20card%20is%20issued%20by%20the%20United%20Nations%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Refugees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Fatima%20said%20the%20police%20detained%20Saleem%E2%80%99s%20wife%20and%20elder%20son%20along%20with%20more%20than%20150%20refugees%20living%20in%20Jammu%20after%20summoning%20them%20for%20verification.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20Rohingya%20refugees%20detained%20were%20sent%20to%20Hira%20Nagar%20jail%2C%20which%20was%20notified%20as%20a%20holding%20centre%20on%20March%205%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20J%26amp%3BK%20government%20had%20then%20said%20in%20a%20notification%20that%20%E2%80%9Call%20illegal%20immigrants%20detected%20by%20law%20enforcement%20agencies%20will%20be%20lodged%20in%20the%20said%20holding%20centre%20and%20it%20shall%20be%20ensured%20that%20these%20persons%20are%20physically%20available%20at%20all%20times%20for%20their%20expeditious%20deportation%20as%20soon%20as%20travel%20documents%20are%20issued%20after%20due%20process%20of%20their%20nationality%20verification%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Saleem%E2%80%99s%20relatives%2C%20the%20couple%20reunited%20in%20the%20Hira%20Nagar%20detention%20centre%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSaleem%20was%20lodged%20in%20the%20district%20jail%20Jammu.%20He%20was%20shifted%20to%20Hira%20Nagar%20detention%20centre%20nearly%20two%20months%20after%20Numina%20was%20detained%2C%E2%80%9D%20Fatima%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20had%20two%20more%20children%20at%20the%20detention%20centre%2C%20including%20the%20baby%20who%20died%20on%20July%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Jammu%2C%20several%20rightwing%20groups%20including%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janta%20Party%20have%20been%20campaigning%20for%20the%20ouster%20of%20Rohingya%20refugees%2C%20claiming%20that%20they%20are%20a%20threat%20to%20demography%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690354855000%2C%22visual%2