servation%20was%20among%20the%20first%20seeds%20sowed%20for%20what%20is%20now%20known%20as%20the%20Montessori%20method%2C%20which%2C%20over%20a%20century%20later%2C%20has%20spread%20far%20and%20wide%20across%20the%20world%20and%20to%20children%20across%20the%20spectrum.%20It%20encourages%20a%20%E2%80%98different%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98informal%E2%80%99%20way%20of%20learning.%20Though%20acknowledged%20to%20have%20both%20pros%20and%20cons%2C%20Dr%20Montessori%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20pioneered%20early%20childhood%20education%20in%20a%20way%20that%20helps%20children%20develop%20their%20own%20pace%20and%20learning%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20820px)%20100vw%2C%20820px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmaria-montessori-1-1690290985.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Maria%20Montessori%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmaria-montessori-1-1690290985.jpg%20820w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmaria-montessori-1-1690290985-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmaria-montessori-1-1690290985-500x282.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmaria-montessori-1-1690290985-768x433.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fmaria-montessori-1-1690290985-150x85.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325135%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22462%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWhen%20Maria%20Montessori%20began%20her%20work%2C%20it%20was%20for%20disabled%20children.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJo%20Chopra-McGowan%2C%20who%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F178695%2Fbeng