seven%20years%20when%20her%20husband%20died.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNeither%20did%20my%20%3Cem%3Epeehar%20%3C%2Fem%3E(father%E2%80%99s%20home)%20nor%20my%20in-laws%20support%20me%20in%20raising%20my%20children.%20So%2C%20after%20my%20husband%E2%80%99s%20death%2C%20I%20had%20to%20withdraw%20them%20from%20their%20English%20medium%20school%20and%20enrol%20them%20in%20a%20government-run%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20ends%20meet%2C%20Shashi%20washed%20tourists%E2%80%99%20clothes%20until%202008%20when%20she%20had%20a%20visitor%20from%20Ireland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20told%20us%20that%20he%20admires%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311742%2Fgujarat-woman-chef-fought-stereotypes-to-start-secret-kitchen-restaurant-australia-aanal-kotak%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20lot.%20And%20since%20he%20was%20our%20guest%2C%20I%20thought%20of%20offering%20him%20the%20food%20we%20had.%20I%20did%20not%20have%20sufficient%20means%2C%20so%20I%20could%20only%20serve%20him%20%3Cem%3Eroti%20sabzi%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebut%20he%20said%20it%20was%20delicious.%20He%20was%20in%20Udaipur%20for%20four%20to%20five%20days%20and%20he%20visited%20us%20each%20day.%20I%20would%20cook%20various%20vegetables%20for%20him%20and%20he%20relished%20them%20all.%20He%20even%20wanted%20to%20learn%20how%20the%20food%20was%20cooked%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20incident%20gave%20her%20the%20idea%20to%20start%20cooking%20classes%20for%20tourists%20and%20%E2%80%98Shashi%20Cooking%20Classes%E2%80%99%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHer%20%E2%80%98English%20Vinglish%E2%80%99%20Moment%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20her%20initial%20experience%20of%20setting%20up%20the%20class%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20have%20a%20good%20kitchen.%20We%20just%20had%20a%20small%20wooden%20table.%20Our%20first%20guest%20was%20an%20Australian%20couple.%20I%20was%20so%20nervous%2C%20my%20hands%20were%20shaking%20and%20I%20was%20also%20sweating.%20I%20even%20dropped%20a%20teacup%2C%20but%20they%20encouraged%20me%20by%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20okay%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shashi%20runs%20cooking%20classes%20to%20teach%20Indian%20cuisine%20to%20foreign%20tourists.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-1-1689859194-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324596%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShashi%20runs%20cooking%20classes%20to%20teach%20Indian%20cuisine%20to%20foreign%20tourists.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20my%20next%20class%2C%20there%20were%20French%20tourists.%20They%20did%20not%20know%20English%20and%20I%20did%20not%20know%20French.%20They%20would%20look%20at%20my%20face%2C%20I%20would%20look%20at%20theirs!%20If%20they%20said%20%3Cem%3Edekho%3C%2Fem%3E%20(%3Cem%3Ed%E2%80%99accord%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20French%20means%20%E2%80%98okay%E2%80%99%20and%20%3Cem%3Edekho%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Hindi%20means%20%E2%80%98see%E2%80%99)%2C%20I%20would%20start%20staring%20at%20places%20and%20everyone%20would%20burst%20into%20laughter%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares%20amidst%20giggles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20language%20barriers%2C%20Shashi%20received%20much%20affection%20from%20foreign%20guests%20who%20also%20tried%20to%20teach%20her%20their%20languages.%20From%20knowing%20only%20Rajasthani%2C%20she%20can%20now%20speak%20basic%20words%20in%20English%20and%20several%20other%20foreign%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20learn%20these%20languages%20because%2C%20without%20that%2C%20it%20would%20be%20difficult%20to%20explain%20my%20cooking%20methods%20to%20foreigners.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20learnt%20that%20%3Cem%3Eaata%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20known%20as%20whole%20wheat%20flour%20in%20English%20and%20%3Cem%3Efarine%20de%20bl%C3%A9%20entier%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20French%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%2C%20while%20carefully%20pronouncing%20the%20words.%20To%20memorise%20them%2C%20she%20would%20write%20all%20these%20words%20in%20Hindi%20in%20her%20diary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20Recipe%20to%20Success%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20admirers%20of%20Indian%20cuisine%20reach%20Shashi%20Cooking%20Classes%20through%20local%20guides%2C%20tour%20operators%2C%20and%20bloggers.%20Shashi%20first%20teaches%20them%20how%20to%20prepare%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20chai%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20then%20moves%20on%20to%20%3Cem%3Echutneys%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20coriander%20and%20dried%20mango%2C%20followed%20by%20%3Cem%3Epakoras%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20paneer%2C%20potatoes%2C%20and%20mixed%20vegetables.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-4-1689859582.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shashi%20has%20trained%20at