0768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-3-1689772598-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324382%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPortia%20started%20with%20three%20children%20which%20has%20now%20grown%20to%2010.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Portia%20Putatunda%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20started%20her%20boarding%20school%20with%20three%20children%20and%20the%20number%20has%20grown%20to%2010%20presently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECalling%20herself%20%E2%80%9Cmother%E2%80%9D%20to%20those%20children%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20children%20are%20not%20orphans%20and%20are%20not%20abandoned%20by%20choice%20but%20by%20poverty.%20Around%2050%20percent%20of%20these%20kids%20do%20not%20have%20a%20surviving%20parent%2C%20but%20the%20rest%20have%20parents%20who%20can%E2%80%99t%20raise%20them.%20This%20is%20where%20I%20come%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20children%20keep%20me%20going%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20morning%20Portia%20wakes%20up%20to%20the%20sound%20of%20the%20children%20outside%20her%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20would%20call%20me%20Portia%20madam%20and%20giggle%20at%20my%20window.%20I%20believe%20this%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20wake%20up%20every%20morning.%20After%20waking%20up%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20I%20do%20is%20to%20light%20up%20the%20tandoor%20to%20heat%20up%20the%20classrooms%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20firewood%20or%20cow%20dung%20for%20the%20tandoor%20and%20I%20cook%20on%20top%20of%20that%20sometimes.%20I%20prepare%20breakfast%20and%20the%20kids%20get%20ready%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20children%20start%20their%20day%20with%20a%20small%20assembly%20and%20then%20head%20to%20their%20classes.%20%E2%80%9CI%20teach%20them%20everything%20from%20mathematics%20and%20science%20to%20English%20and%20art.%20I%20also%20conduct%20many%20activities%20like%20gardening%2C%20dancing%2C%20etc%20throughout%20the%20week%20to%20keep%20the%20learning%20wholesome%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20children%E2%80%99s%20age%20group%20is%20between%20three%20and%2010%20years%20old.%20The%20classes%20go%20up%20to%205%20o%E2%80%99clock%20in%20the%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-4-1689772663.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Portia's%20classroom%20in%20Komic%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-4-1689772663.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-4-1689772663-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-4-1689772663-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-4-1689772663-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-4-1689772663-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324385%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPortia%20left%20her%20journalism%20career%20to%20become%20a%20teacher%20and%20%E2%80%9Cmother%E2%80%9D%20to%20these%20underprivileged%20children.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Portia%20Putatunda%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20girl%2C%20who%20is%20older%20than%20other%20children%2C%20takes%20one%20class%20at%20my%20school.%20She%20used%20to%20be%20very%20shy.%20But%20today%2C%20she%20helps%20me%20in%20taking%20care%20of%20the%20children%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20hurdles%20she%20faces%20regularly%2C%20Portia%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20main%20issue%20that%20I%20have%20been%20facing%20for%20quite%20some%20time%20is%20funding.%20I%20built%20this%20place%20with%20my%20savings%20and%20there%20have%20been%20months%20when%20I%20am%20unsure%20how%20I%20will%20buy%20vegetables%20and%20food%20for%20us.%20However%2C%20something%20or%20the%20other%20always%20works%20out%20and%20we%20end%20up%20having%20just%20enough%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20concerns%20have%20always%20been%20%E2%80%94%20what%20next%3F%20I%20have%20always%20had%20this%20feeling%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98aukaat%20se%20bahar%20ki%20zimmedari%20leli%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Did%20I%20take%20up%20a%20responsibility%20that%20I%20am%20not%20capable%20of%20fulfilling%3F).%20I%20am%20capable%20of%20undertaking%20the%20primary%20education%20of%20these%20kids.%20But%20I%20am%20looking%20at%20prospective%20schools%20which%20can%20take%20them%20in%20when%20they%20will%20need%20secondary%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSelf-doubts%20keep%20bothering%20me%2C%20but%20what%20keeps%20me%20going%20is%20the%20smile%20on%20all%20these%20little%20faces.%20These%20children%20are%20so%20untouched%20and%20pure.%20I%20believe%20that%20I%20am%20just%20a%20medium%2C%20and%20it%20was%20the%20fate%20of%20these%20kids%20that%20brought%20me%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20850px)%20100vw%2C%20850px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-7-1689774500.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Portia%20with%20the%20kids%20she%20teaches%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22850%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-7-1689774500.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-7-1689774500