20works%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20a%20network%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F124905%2Fartificial-intelligence-cctv-cameras-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-resolution%20cameras%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20are%20strategically%20placed%20on%20the%20car.%20These%20cameras%20capture%20real-time%20images%20of%20their%20surroundings%20and%20transmit%20them%20to%20the%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291211%2Fiit-palakkad-offers-free-course-on-artificial-intelligence-ai-how-to-apply%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20AI%20System%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20system%20makes%20decisions%20based%20on%20these%20images%20and%20drives%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20ecosystem%20for%20an%20autonomous%20vehicle%20in%20India.%20So%20when%20we%20took%20on%20the%20task%20of%20building%20an%20autonomous%20vehicle%2C%20we%20also%20took%20up%20the%20task%20of%20building%20up%20an%20ecosystem%20around%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gursimran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20also%20believe%20that%20the%20car%20is%20also%20a%20step%20towards%20safer%20roads%20as%20it%20eliminates%20the%20risks%20of%20human%20errors%20while%20driving.%20zPod%20can%20drive%20on%20any%20kind%20of%20environmental%20or%20geographical%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20duo%20was%20confident%20about%20their%20design%2C%20others%20were%20unsure%20if%20India%20was%20the%20right%20place%20to%20launch%20the%20vehicle.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20many%20people%20who%20questioned%20us%20and%20asked%20us%20to%20move%20our%20innovation%20to%20a%20developed%20country%2C%20but%20we%20wanted%20to%20make%20it%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gagandeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20raised%201.7%20million%20dollars%20in%20seed%20funding%20from%20various%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%